<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>AI Frontier — 트랙 선택 가이드</title>
<style>
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  :root {
    --brand: #F97316;
    --brand-dark: #EA580C;
    --brand-light: #FFF7ED;
    --brand-mid: #FFEDD5;
    /* Track A: 데이터 분석 자동화 (파랑) */
    --t1: #3B82F6;
    --t1-light: #EFF6FF;
    --t1-mid: #DBEAFE;
    /* Track B: 프로그램 빌드 (보라) */
    --t2: #8B5CF6;
    --t2-light: #F5F3FF;
    --t2-mid: #EDE9FE;
    --gray-50: #FAFAF9;
    --gray-100: #F5F5F4;
    --gray-200: #E7E5E4;
    --gray-300: #D6D3D1;
    --gray-400: #A8A29E;
    --gray-500: #78716C;
    --gray-600: #57534E;
    --gray-700: #44403C;
    --gray-800: #292524;
    --gray-900: #1C1917;
    --radius: 16px;
    --radius-sm: 10px;
  }

  body {
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
    background: var(--gray-50);
    color: var(--gray-800);
    line-height: 1.6;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 24px 20px 80px;
  }

  .top-bar {
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--brand), #FB923C);
  }

  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 48px 20px 40px;
  }
  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--brand);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--gray-900);
    line-height: 1.35;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .hero p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    max-width: 440px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section {
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .section-label {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--brand);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .track-cards {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .track-card {
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 24px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .track-card.t1 {
    background: var(--t1-light);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--t1-mid);
  }
  .track-card.t2 {
    background: var(--t2-light);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--t2-mid);
  }
  .track-num {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .track-card.t1 .track-num { color: var(--t1); }
  .track-card.t2 .track-num { color: var(--t2); }
  .track-card h3 {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gray-900);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .track-card .subtitle {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .track-card .keywords {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 6px;
    margin-top: 14px;
  }
  .track-card .keywords span {
    font-size: 12px;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .track-card.t1 .keywords span {
    background: var(--t1-mid);
    color: var(--t1);
  }
  .track-card.t2 .keywords span {
    background: var(--t2-mid);
    color: var(--t2);
  }

  /* 공통 Day 1 배너 */
  .common-banner {
    background: var(--brand-light);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--brand-mid);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 20px 22px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .common-day {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--brand);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .common-desc {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .common-flow {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .common-flow span {
    font-size: 12px;
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--brand-mid);
    color: var(--gray-700);
    padding: 5px 10px;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  .common-note {
    font-size: 12.5px;
    color: var(--brand-dark);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 12px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* 트랙별 커리큘럼 카드 */
  .curri-cards {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .curri-card {
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 20px 22px;
    border: 1.5px solid;
  }
  .curri-card.t1 { background: var(--t1-light); border-color: var(--t1-mid); }
  .curri-card.t2 { background: var(--t2-light); border-color: var(--t2-mid); }
  .curri-head {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .curri-card.t1 .curri-head { color: var(--t1); }
  .curri-card.t2 .curri-head { color: var(--t2); }
  .curri-goal {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .curri-day { margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .curri-day:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .curri-day-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    color: var(--gray-400);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .curri-day ul { list-style: none; }
  .curri-day li {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--gray-700);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    padding-left: 14px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .curri-day li::before {
    content: '·';
    position: absolute;
    left: 4px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .checklist {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--gray-200);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .checklist-header {
    padding: 24px 24px 0;
  }
  .checklist-header h2 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gray-900);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .checklist-header p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .checklist-items {
    padding: 0 12px 12px;
  }
  .check-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 14px 12px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.15s;
    user-select: none;
    -webkit-user-select: none;
  }
  .check-item:hover {
    background: var(--gray-50);
  }
  .check-item.checked {
    background: var(--gray-50);
  }
  .check-item.checked[data-track="1"] {
    background: var(--t1-light);
  }
  .check-item.checked[data-track="2"] {
    background: var(--t2-light);
  }
  .checkbox {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 22px;
    height: 22px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 2px solid var(--gray-300);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: all 0.15s;
    margin-top: 1px;
  }
  .check-item.checked[data-track="1"] .checkbox {
    background: var(--t1);
    border-color: var(--t1);
  }
  .check-item.checked[data-track="2"] .checkbox {
    background: var(--t2);
    border-color: var(--t2);
  }
  .checkbox svg {
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.15s;
  }
  .check-item.checked .checkbox svg {
    opacity: 1;
  }
  .check-label {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--gray-700);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .progress-bar {
    margin: 20px 24px 0;
    padding-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .progress-track {
    height: 6px;
    background: var(--gray-100);
    border-radius: 100px;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
  }
  .progress-fill-t1 {
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--t1);
    transition: width 0.3s ease;
    width: 0%;
  }
  .progress-fill-t2 {
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--t2);
    transition: width 0.3s ease;
    width: 0%;
  }
  .progress-labels {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-top: 8px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .progress-labels .l1 { color: var(--t1); }
  .progress-labels .l2 { color: var(--t2); }

  .result-area {
    margin-top: 24px;
  }
  .result-card {
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 32px 24px;
    text-align: center;
    display: none;
    animation: fadeUp 0.4s ease;
  }
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  .result-card.show { display: block; }
  .result-card.t1-result {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--t1-light), #DBEAFE);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--t1-mid);
  }
  .result-card.t2-result {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--t2-light), #EDE9FE);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--t2-mid);
  }
  .result-card.tie-result {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--t1-light), var(--t2-light));
    border: 1.5px solid var(--gray-200);
  }
  .result-icon {
    font-size: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .result-card h3 {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .result-card.t1-result h3 { color: var(--t1); }
  .result-card.t2-result h3 { color: var(--t2); }
  .result-card.tie-result h3 { color: var(--gray-700); }
  .result-card .result-sub {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .result-examples {
    text-align: left;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 16px 18px;
  }
  .result-examples .ex-title {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gray-400);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.8px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .result-examples li {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    padding-left: 4px;
    list-style: none;
  }
  .result-examples li::before {
    content: '· ';
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .empty-state {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 32px;
    color: var(--gray-400);
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .examples-section {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--gray-200);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .examples-header {
    padding: 24px 24px 16px;
  }
  .examples-header h2 {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gray-900);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .examples-header p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--gray-500);
  }
  .example-columns {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--gray-100);
  }
  .example-col {
    padding: 16px 20px;
  }
  .example-col:first-child {
    border-right: 1px solid var(--gray-100);
  }
  .example-col-title {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .example-col-title.c1 { color: var(--t1); }
  .example-col-title.c2 { color: var(--t2); }
  .example-col li {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
  }
  .example-col li::before {
    content: '· ';
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .examples-footer {
    padding: 16px 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--gray-100);
  }

  /* Ambiguous pairs */
  .ambiguous-pairs {
    padding: 20px 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--gray-100);
  }
  .ap-title {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gray-800);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .ap-subtitle {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .ap-group {
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .ap-group:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .ap-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gray-400);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .ap-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .ap-row:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .ap-row.to-a { background: var(--t1-light); }
  .ap-row.to-b { background: var(--t2-light); }
  .ap-scenario {
    flex: 1;
    color: var(--gray-700);
    line-height: 1.45;
  }
  .ap-arrow {
    color: var(--gray-400);
    font-weight: 600;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .ap-badge {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: #fff;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .ap-row.to-a .ap-badge { background: var(--t1); }
  .ap-row.to-b .ap-badge { background: var(--t2); }

  .tip {
    background: var(--brand-light);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--brand-mid);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 20px 24px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .tip-icon {
    font-size: 20px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 1px;
  }
  .tip-content {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--gray-700);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .tip-content strong {
    color: var(--gray-900);
  }

  .result-day1-note {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin-top: 20px;
    padding-top: 16px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .reset-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    background: none;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--gray-200);
    border-radius: 100px;
    padding: 8px 18px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    cursor: pointer;
    margin-top: 16px;
    transition: all 0.15s;
  }
  .reset-btn:hover {
    border-color: var(--brand);
    color: var(--brand-dark);
  }

  .footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px 20px 20px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--gray-400);
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .container { padding: 16px 16px 60px; }
    .hero { padding: 36px 12px 32px; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 22px; }
    .checklist-header { padding: 20px 20px 0; }
    .checklist-items { padding: 0 8px 8px; }
    .check-item { padding: 12px 10px; }
    .progress-bar { margin: 16px 20px 0; }
    .examples-header { padding: 20px 20px 12px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="top-bar"></div>

<div class="container">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-badge">AI Frontier 2026</div>
    <h1>나에게 맞는 트랙은?</h1>
    <p>Day 1은 공통, <strong>Day 2~3</strong>은 2개 트랙으로 나뉩니다.<br>내 업무 성향으로 맞는 트랙을 자동 추천받아 보세요.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Track Intro -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">Day 2~3 · 2개 트랙</div>
    <div class="track-cards">
      <div class="track-card t1">
        <div class="track-num">Track A</div>
        <h3>데이터 분석 자동화</h3>
        <div class="subtitle">데이터로 <strong>분석하고, 인사이트 뽑고, 보고서·대시보드로</strong> 자동 출력하는 분석 파이프라인</div>
        <div class="keywords">
          <span>pandas</span>
          <span>데이터 분석</span>
          <span>시각화</span>
          <span>보고서 자동화</span>
          <span>Streamlit 대시보드</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="track-card t2">
        <div class="track-num">Track B</div>
        <h3>프로그램 빌드</h3>
        <div class="subtitle">반복 업무를 대신하는 <strong>실행 프로그램·AI 도구</strong>를 직접 설계·빌드·배포하는 End-to-End 시스템</div>
        <div class="keywords">
          <span>Cursor 심화</span>
          <span>프로그램 설계</span>
          <span>PyQt GUI</span>
          <span>.exe 빌드</span>
          <span>AI 챗봇·유틸</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Curriculum at a glance -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">커리큘럼 한눈에</div>

    <!-- Common Day 1 -->
    <div class="common-banner">
      <div class="common-day">Day 1 · 공통</div>
      <div class="common-desc">두 트랙 모두 함께 듣습니다</div>
      <div class="common-flow">
        <span>Cursor · Python 세팅</span>
        <span>데이터 · AI 개념 + 보안</span>
        <span>프롬프트 · Canvas</span>
        <span>pandas · ipynb 기초</span>
        <span>개인정보 탐색 (AI Agent)</span>
        <span>PRD · 트랙 선택</span>
      </div>
      <div class="common-note">↓ Day 1 마지막 '과제 정의 워크숍 &amp; 트랙 선택'에서 트랙을 정합니다</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Track curriculum cards -->
    <div class="curri-cards">
      <div class="curri-card t1">
        <div class="curri-head">Track A · 데이터 분석 자동화</div>
        <div class="curri-goal">데이터 → 분석 · 인사이트 · 보고까지 자동화하는 파이프라인 설계·구현</div>
        <div class="curri-day">
          <div class="curri-day-label">Day 2</div>
          <ul>
            <li>데이터 집계·분석 (pandas) + matplotlib · seaborn 시각화</li>
            <li>python-pptx · docx로 PPT · Word 보고서 자동화</li>
            <li>Streamlit 대시보드 · PyQt GUI 도구 제작</li>
            <li>윈도우 스케줄러로 정기 보고서 자동 실행</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="curri-day">
          <div class="curri-day-label">Day 3</div>
          <ul>
            <li>Gemini API 챗봇 + SMTP 첨부파일 자동 메일 발송</li>
            <li>본인 과제 PRD 작성 · 해결 방향성 도출</li>
            <li>프로토타입 + 프로젝트 개요서 1p + 1:1 피드백</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="curri-card t2">
        <div class="curri-head">Track B · 프로그램 빌드</div>
        <div class="curri-goal">AI Agent를 설계·구현해 즉시 적용 가능한 End-to-End 자동화 시스템 구축</div>
        <div class="curri-day">
          <div class="curri-day-label">Day 2</div>
